{"tid":748634,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救!換左主機用唔到雙MON","createTime":"2018-07-19T11:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T05:57:11.000Z","uid":80308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb65246a00d54acecb2dfb5c5a0e54564b6dd4b","tid":748634,"uid":80308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:09:39.000Z","msg":"本身部機既SETTING係咁:<br />\n<br />\n主機display port out --&gt; Mon 1既mini display port in,<br />\nMon 1 既display port out--&gt;再去Mon 2既mini display port in<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家換左機,無display port,得HDMI,<br />\n<br />\n主機HDMI--&gt;Mon 1既HDMI,<br />\nMon 1 display port out--&gt;去Mon 2 mini display port in<br />\n<br />\n兩個mon都係dell U2417H型號,<br />\n而家得MON 1有畫面,MON 2連接唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以幫下我,我係電腦白痴,研究左好耐都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f2c2b4f85df6dfad8294de808dec7189e32a86","tid":748634,"uid":31990,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"點解唔喺主機out晒去mon1同2，要由mon1 out去2咁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新機有無顯示卡？"},{"pid":"b6611dae86bced82555c01cd894a1af2c5b96cf2","tid":748634,"uid":116836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:12:18.000Z","msg":"$20收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a32628f7dada28063fb155ac5a9e28c2f235386","tid":748634,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:15:05.000Z","msg":"去控制台搞咪得，聽你咁講應該之前個display setting係由mon1延伸去mon2"},{"pid":"56590173cb39d070306967a2abbc165b8ed6ea4a","tid":748634,"uid":80308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor